AROS PORT of MESA: THE OPENGL SOFTWARE EMULATION by Kalamatee
====================================================================
After hearing of the lack of 3d softwar on AROS i decided to try and get one of the amiga
ports up and running..

For AROS or the Amiga there are only three important files + one directory.

src/AmigaMesa.c         The Mesa GL Amiga/AROS implementation 
			      (ddsample.c with some Amiga code)
src-tk/AWindow.c        The TK (and AUX) machine specific code.
include/GL/AmigaMesa.h	The prototypes for AmigaMesa.

